patthana8.65:1.1_0: Nasukhasahagataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:2.1_0: Nanasukhasahagataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nanasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:3.1_0: Nasukhasahagatañca nanasukhasahagatañca dhammaṁ paṭicca nasukhasahagato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
patthana8.65:4.1_0: Hetuyā nava …pe… purejāte āsevane cha …pe… avigate nava.
